data.description: Move-in ready 2-2-1 manufactured home in Holly Park West! This home has a covered front deck, enclosed back deck, attached garage with separate storage room...it has it all! NO LOT RENT! Wired for security system, just need to activate with Vivent. Motion sensor light above garage stays. Outdoor ramp to the front door stays. New roof installed in 2016. Square footage does not reflect 112 sq ft of finished garage space. Located in desirable Fruita, this is a rare opportunity to purchase a home with a garage in Holly Park West! Schedule your showing today!
